'''Johannes Age "Joop" Bakker ''' (27 May 1921 – 3 October 2003) was a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] politician of the defunct [[Anti-Revolutionary Party]] (ARP) now merged into the [[Christian Democratic Appeal]] (CDA).<ref>{{nl icon}} {{cite web|url=https://www.trouw.nl/home/het-eerste-gekleurde-overhemd~afc11691/|title=Het eerste gekleurde overhemd|publisher=Trouw|date=8 October 2003|accessdate=26 November 2018}}</ref>

