'''TEAM2 cluster''' is a [[France|French]] [[business cluster]] for environmental technologies and circular economy. It is located in Northern France in [[Urban Community of Lille Métropole]] and at [[Loos-en-Gohelle]]. It is supported by [[Université Lille Nord de France]], [[Veolia Environnement]], [[Suez Environnement]] and 200 SMEs.
